Cooked slimy eels are a type of fish that can be obtained by cooking raw slimy eels on a fire or cooking range, requiring level 28 Cooking and granting 95 experience when successful. Players may burn a slimy eel while cooking one, resulting in a burnt eel; the burn rate while cooking these will decrease as players reach higher Cooking levels. It will stop burning entirely at Cooking level 61 on both ranges and fires. When eaten, slimy eels heal between 6 and 10 hitpoints.

A regular fishing rod and fishing bait are required to catch them. It can only be caught in the Mort Myre Swamp and in the Lumbridge Swamp Caves.
